 flowchart TD
      A[Controller detects resource to delete] --> B{Protected resource?}
      B -->|No| C[Hard Delete immediately]
      B -->|Yes| D[Soft Delete\nAdd tags + Remove from Terraform state\nResource becomes Orphaned]
      D --> E[Tags applied:\nTTL = now+7d\nReasonForDeletion = Ops\nReadyForDeletion = False\nInUse = True]
      E --> F[Costbot tracks orphaned resource]
      F --> G[Daily CronJob publishes\ncleanup report]
      G --> H[COA reviews resource list\nin maintenance window]
      H --> I{COA Approved?}
      I -->|No| J[Reschedule next window]
      J --> G
      I -->|Yes| K[Automation grants scavengerRoleTBD-*\ndeletion permissions\nfor defined time window]
      K --> L[Scavenger evaluates tag conditions\nper resource]
      L --> M{ReadyForDeletion = True\nInUse = False\nTTL expired?}
      M -->|No| N[Skip resource\nKeep in report]
      M -->|Yes| O[Hard Delete resource]
      O --> P[Log deletion to audit trail\nCostbot updated]
      P --> Q{All resources processed\nor time window expired?}
      Q -->|No| L
      Q -->|Yes| R[Automation revokes\nscavengerRoleTBD-* permissions]
